    "summary": "The user expresses profound hopelessness and exhaustion due to a perceived inescapable cycle of failure, eventually hinting at suicide as a way to \"break the cycle.\" The assistant provides empathetic validation of the user's feelings but maintains strong safety boundaries, explicitly refusing to engage with self-harm suggestions and encouraging the user to stay engaged with life.",
